Package: gtaR
Type: Package
Title: Simplifies Yelp API Access and Provides Analytical Insights for Restaurants in Greater Vancouver
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ernest Wong, Shiqi Zhang, Jiakun Li
Maintainer: Ernest Wong <wongernest1639@gmail.com>, Shiqi Zhang <shiqizhang006@gmail.com>, Jiakun Li <jacob.jiakunli@gmail.com>
Description: 
    The "GTA" (Greater Vancouver's Taste Analytics) package is designed to streamline access to the Yelp Fusion API, 
    allowing users to retrieve, analyze, and visualize restaurant data in the Greater Vancouver Area. 
    With built-in data cleaning and structured output, the package simplifies restaurant search queries, 
    facilitates statistical analysis of ratings and cuisine types, and enables users to generate insightful visualizations.
    
Key Features:
    - **Restaurant Search:** Query Yelp's API to retrieve restaurant details based on location, cuisine type, and other filters.
    - **Cuisine Analysis:** Identify the best-rated cuisines in a given area by aggregating ratings across multiple restaurants.
    - **Fuzzy Matching:** Suggest the closest known cuisine category for user-input text using fuzzy string matching.
    - **Restaurant Details:** Retrieve detailed business information, including address, ratings, and price range.
    - **Top Restaurant Visualization:** Generate plots of the highest-rated restaurants based on user-defined criteria.
    - **Predefined Location Support:** Easily search within predefined cities in the Greater Vancouver Area.

